videos.headline: Memphis runs play-action to perfection for TD
videos.description: Memphis gets Houston to bite on the play-action, leaving Alan Cross wide open for the catch and run into the end zone from 38 yards out increasing the Tigers' lead to 10-0.

videos.headline: Memphis game winning FG attempt goes wide-right
videos.description: With a chance to win the game, Memphis' Jake Elliott pushes his 48-yard field goal attempt to the right, allowing Houston to stay perfect with a 35-34 win.
